meanings: Noun 이름, 성명, 성함 (→assumed name, brand name, code name, family name, first name, forename, household name, maiden name, middle name, nickna...
short for you know what i mean
The thing you put at the start of a comment replying to someone on Youtube. You don't actually put name in it but you replace it with their username.
